These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: juice, tea
1. the person drinking tea is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2   |
| Beverage   | tea | juice |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-2::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  security-guard, freelancer
1. the security-guard is on the left or right of the freelancer##3
2. the freelancer is on the right of the security-guard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |     1     |      2      |
| Job   | security-guard | freelancer |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: card-games, sudoku
1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is card-games##3
2. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |
| Hobby   | sudoku | card-games |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-4::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: indie, disco
1. the fan of disco is on the left of the fan of indie##1
2. the fan of indie is on the left or right of the fan of disco##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |
| Music-Genre   | disco | indie |

